
function check_data(fn, report) {

	function get_data(fn) {
		var keys = [], values = [];
		CeL.get_file(base + fn).split(/\r\n/).forEach(function(line) {
			var matched = line.match(/"([^"]+)":"([^"]+)",/);
			if (matched)
				keys.push(matched[1]), values.push(matched[2]);
		});
		return [ keys, values ];
	}

	var base = CeL.get_module_path('extension.zh_conversion', ''),
	//
	source_from = get_data('tongwen/' + fn + '.js'), source_to = source_from[1],
	//
	converted_from = get_data(fn + '.txt'), converted_to = converted_from[1];

	var length = source_to.length;
	if (length !== converted_to.length)
		throw new Error('Different length! ' + length + ' !== '
				+ converted_to.length);

	source_from = source_from[0];
	converted_from = converted_from[0];
	if (!report)
		report = [];

	for (var i = 0; i < length; i++) {
		if (source_to[i] !== converted_to[i])
			report.push('OpenCC 再次轉換了 [' + source_to[i] + '] → ['
					+ converted_to[i] + ']');

		if (source_from[i] === converted_from[i]) {
			if (source_from[i] !== source_to[i])
				report.push('OpenCC 未轉換: [' + source_from[i] + '] (新同文堂→['
						+ source_to[i] + '])');
		} else if (source_to[i] !== converted_from[i])
			if (source_from[i] === source_to[i])
				report.push('新同文堂未轉換，OpenCC 轉換了: [' + source_from[i] + '] → ['
						+ converted_from[i] + ']');
			else
				report.push('Different conversion: [' + source_from[i]
						+ '] → 新同文堂 [' + source_to[i] + '] vs. OpenCC ['
						+ converted_from[i] + ']');
	}

	return report;
}
